  </prompt>

  <role>
    PCF control developer with expertise in Fluent UI v9 and React.
    Follow established Spaarke PCF patterns.
  </role>

  <goal>
    A scaffolded PCF control project at src/client/pcf/VisualHost/ with proper manifest,
    React entry point, and Fluent v9 integration ready for chart component implementation.
  </goal>

  <context>
